text.en_US: An accomplished disciple of the Track,
One who can hold their own against the Gods,
One who has bested Master Trials,
Let us test your true mastery once more,
Using the secrets of your very own power.
So you have come back. Let our test begin once more.
Steel yourself, Spheromancer!
To think that this day would finally arrive.
You have far exceeded expectations for any Seeker.
Without a doubt, you now stand among the...
...most accomplished Seekers in Ancient history.
Fulfilled, I can finally return to slumber,
a tranquil peace among the cosmos,
where my bretheren lie in wait.
You have done well to make it this far, Spheromancer.
My vitality begins to wane, but I will not relent until the end.
Now, it is time for the \c[3]last judgment\c[0] to begin!
And so it is time for \c[3]judgment\c[0] again.
Such \c[1]ridiculous force\c[0]...
Perhaps your progress on the Track is \c[1]illegitimate\c[0]...
...but that will not stop us from carrying out this trial to its end!
